{"tid":812662,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］用口健樂真係番唔到轉頭","createTime":"2018-09-09T22:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T01:21:26.000Z","uid":43738,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1f9f574e7a9ffec43a71a9401988265d4e1a2f49","tid":812662,"uid":43738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T22:52:25.000Z","msg":"前日生左2粒痱滋用左佢 <br />\n一粒細既好番  但粒中size既  無好不特止仲一變三<br />\n直到頭先一直痛到瞓唔著  我就用多次  <br />\n我用開都識搽份量  含完水點知一路都好乸  <br />\n照鏡睇啲痱滋吸晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    一直無停過係咁刺痛 <br />\n我即刻係咁「long」口唔得 痛到我頂唔順用牙刷想刷番走晒又唔得 <br />\n之後而家成part出血  到底點可以整番走啲口健樂 ！！<br />\n仲要番工 好想瞓但痛到瞓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人試過"},{"pid":"cb15bfaa98fb2bf147e2da9f6ffc9b7f2c6b3a69","tid":812662,"uid":17680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T23:45:39.000Z","msg":"你用牙刷去刷 唔流都變流啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8d0937ee075ec36dddc5d9cfe9e83e6df66c31","tid":812662,"uid":172024,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T00:50:18.000Z","msg":"吸哂入去咪證明work囉 <br />\n刺痛係正常啦 果個係傷口黎架喎 <br />\n仲要比你用牙刷刷佢 無血就奇啦 <br />\n仲話用開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64591dc31a6e1dc8ac8344d6c5d3796a0a4ed469","tid":812662,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T01:09:19.000Z","msg":"下次生痱滋 試下用益達士多啤梨個隻鐵盒糖<br />\n含住係粒痱滋到 含到熔 第二日就會好返"},{"pid":"844f28df5eeb42a775c7695c9d99e881ce7b15c2","tid":812662,"uid":183798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"64591dc31a6e1dc8ac8344d6c5d3796a0a4ed469","tid":812662,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T01:09:19.000Z","msg":"下次生痱滋 試下用益達士多啤梨個隻鐵盒糖<br />\n含